I"Ñ<p>Coinberg is an application that fetches holdings from various blockchain wallets (bitcoin, ethereum, dash, and neo), and aggregates their value.</p>

<p>The first technical goal of this project was to learn EmberJS to complete my front-end development skills. The second technical goal was to migrate the Ruby-on-Rails codebase into an Elixir/Phoenix codebase to learn and improve the app performance.</p>

